title: Robocop (1995)(Bitloks)(1920).mkv
description:
Detroit - in the future - is crime-ridden, and run by a massive company. The company have developed a huge crime-fighting robot, which unfortunately develops a rather dangerous glitch. The company sees a way to get back in favor with the public when a cop called Alex Murphy is killed by a street gang. Murphy's body is reconstructed within a steel shell and named RoboCop. The RoboCop is very successful against criminals, and becomes a target of supervillain Boddicker.

The original disc has varying levels of quality. Some scenes are as expected and others look like an up-scaled VHS.
